        </div>
Chuko ramen is looking for part time and potential full time servers to join the team at our soon to be open Bushwick location. <br>
<br>
Applicants must be friendly, knowledgeable, efficient and work well as part of a team. Brooklyn server experience is preferred. A sense of humor is also greatly appreciated! We are accepting resumes via email ONLY. Please post resume in body of email, and include availability. No attachments will be opened. No walk in resumes will be considered. No phone calls. Please inquire if interested. Thanks!<br>
<br>
Chuko provides equal employment opportunities (EEO) to all applicants for employment without regard to race, color, religion, gender, sexual orientation, national origin, age, disability, genetic information, marital status, amnesty, or status as covered veteran in accordance with applicable federal, state &amp; local laws.    </section>

